All files from the original lua-5.1.4.tar.gz release are unchanged.  The
following files have been added:

	luavs.bat - copied from etc/luavs.bat and modified to build Lua
	            as C++, as needed by Iguana.
        win32/    - 32-bit versions of lua51.lib and lua51.dll.
	win64/    - 64-bit versions of same.
